snippet.title: Shaq Fu: A Legend Reborn - Launch Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/shaq-fu-a-legend-reborn-ps4/

The day of our deliverance has arrived! Shaq Fu: A Legend Reborn is Now Available on PS4!

Shaq Fu: A Legend Reborn is an intense, combo-fueled, side-scrolling beat-‘em-up brawler starring and voiced by Shaq himself.

https://www.alegendreborn.com/
